{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-435-polynomials-of-fibonacci-numbers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 435: Polinomija za brojeve Fibonaccija","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Nambari za Fibonacci $\\{f_n, n ≥ 0\\}$ zimetangazwa kwa mfululizo kama $f_n = f_{n - 1} + f_{n - 2}$ kwa misingi ya $f_0 = 0$ na $f_1 = 1$.</p>\n<p>Definišite polinomialu $\\{F_n, n ≥ 0\\}$ kao $F_n(x) = \\displaystyle\\sum_{i = 0}^n f_ix^i$.</p>\n<p>Kwa mfano, $F_7(x) = x + x^2 + 2x^3 + 3x^4 + 5x^5 + 8x^6 + 13x^7$, na $F_7(11) = 268\\,357\\,683$.</p>\n<p>Acha $n = {10}^{15}$. Tafuta jumla $\\displaystyle\\sum_{x = 0}^{100} F_n(x)$ na toa jibu lako modulo $1\\,307\\,674\\,368\\,000 \\, (= 15!)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5201000cf542c510032","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302106,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-435-polynomials-of-fibonacci-numbers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function polynomialsOfFibonacciNumbers() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npolynomialsOfFibonacciNumbers();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>polynomialsOfFibonacciNumbers()</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>252541322550</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(polynomialsOfFibonacciNumbers(), 252541322550);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-435-polynomials-of-fibonacci-numbers","certification":"projec